Business Brief -- Corning Inc.:
   Company and Mexican Firm
   Complete Deal for Venture
The new venture -- known in the U.S. as Corning Vitro
Corp. and in Mexico as Vitro Corning S.A. de C.V. -- will
make and distribute such Corning brands as Corning Ware,
Pyrex, Visions, Revere Ware and Corelle, along with Vitro's
glassware and crystal.
   The venture is expected to have annual sales of more than
$800 million.